{"tid":1753402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你知道嗎?勝利是基建於5千多名手足被捕","createTime":"2019-11-25T02:44:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T08:40:51.000Z","uid":121473,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"68eee4ad55b66512ca0205694a223143c194ab58","tid":1753402,"uid":121473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T02:44:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SAMSCZq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSAMSCZq.png&h=aec9f1d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n維基<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">死亡</span> 至少12人[註 2]（截至11月14日）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">受傷</span> 逾1,900人受傷（截至11月20日[註 1]）<br />\n逾2,000人（袁國勇估計截至8月15日[14]）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">被捕</span> 5,804人（截至11月19日[註 3]）<br />\n根據警方公布數字<br />\n6月9日－11月18日：4,491人<br />\n11月19日：1313人<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">刑事指控</span> 521人（截至11月14日）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"065de2e78bd8f91465ac0683603541a5a4396b63","tid":1753402,"uid":222789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T02:44:55.000Z","msg":"血同汗換返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6465ff890f43db58e4181efaac8db4485f7ba2ab","tid":1753402,"uid":38154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T02:48:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"825c79494c86a2c949418b70c878edd2fb1be84b","tid":1753402,"uid":48315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r