1-25T03:02:02.000Z","msg":"【岑子杰呼籲警方解封理大】<br />\n<br />\n社民連岑子杰勝出區選後接受訪問，呼籲其他民主派當選人及高票落選者一同聯署，要求警方盡快解封理大，釋放所有被捕人，並停止對被捕人作政治檢控。他指這是政府應馬上做的第一個讓步。"},{"pid":"702a48825560aa553166f574b5d242840ed5ce4a","tid":1753402,"uid":258109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:05:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d55d1a6018bb18430284a27940e30b6e9aa4bca","tid":1753402,"uid":121473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:43:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e24fc3d02d544d5be899d83145eca7188c9c3d2","tid":1753402,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:45:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"afd1f711fa102f5b2abfa95f688a22d1599452ea","tid":1753402,"uid":45975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:45:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"345734a3708844e7c3d90e172b9aa81653a3d453","tid":1753402,"uid":121473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:36:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43e93e9ed44cb39bad0f844643829036bf4e738f","tid":1753402,"uid":34996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:38:04.000Z","msg":"血票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96479c120854716244fe8b76044f76da01e3e5cd","tid":1753402,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite